mm, vmalloc: remove VM_VPAGES

VM_VPAGES is unnecessary, it's easier to check is_vmalloc_addr() when
reading /proc/vmallocinfo.

[akpm@linux-foundation.org: remove VM_VPAGES reference via kvfree()]
